properties.tooltip: The name of the column that will be the input of the QuantileDiscretizer process.
The name of the column that will be the output of the QuantileDiscretizer process.
Number of buckets (quantiles, or categories) into which data points are grouped. Must be >= 2.

properties.propertyName: Relative target precision (must be between 0 and 1)
properties.tooltip: The relative target precision for the approximate quantile algorithm used to generate buckets. Must be in the range [0, 1].
How to handle invalid entries. Options are skip (filter out rows with invalid values), error (throw an error), or keep (keep invalid values in a special additional bucket).
